name: Hassle Mind 2

Hassle Mind 2 of 3 artwork series

The many uncertainties that occur in this life at this time are like a puzzle or odd pieces of beautiful visual objects, but irregular. I perceive this as an artistic form of the process of making this artwork. I'm trying to re-illustrate pieces of an object into a moving masterpiece.
